      "name": "Hemolysis index validation at 5 L/min, 3000 RPM — no UQ reported",
      "description": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis compared against in-vitro measurement at 5 L/min and 3000 RPM. Predicted NIH = 0.0042 g/100 L; measured NIH = 0.0051 g/100 L. Relative error 17.6%. No uncertainty quantification was performed for this validation result; confidence intervals and sensitivity indices are absent."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/vr-02-pump-6lpm-2800rpm",
