      "description": "CFD-predicted NIH = 0.0038 g/100 L; measured NIH = 0.0049 g/100 L. Relative error 22.4%. Uncertainty quantification was not conducted for this operating point; no Monte Carlo propagation or interval estimates are provided."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/vr-03-pump-4lpm-3200rpm",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Hemolysis index validation at 4 L/min, 3200 RPM — no UQ reported",
      "description": "CFD-predicted NIH = 0.0061 g/100 L; measured NIH = 0.0055 g/100 L. Relative error 10.9%. No uncertainty quantification is attached to this result; epistemic uncertainty in blood damage model coefficients is uncharacterized."
    }
