      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software used for CFD simulation must be validated under a formal SQA plan with documented version control, regression testing, and configuration management consistent with MRL 5 requirements.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (OpenFOAM 8) is used without a formal SQA plan. Version control is present but regression test suite covers only 40% of relevant solver modules. Achieved level 2 versus required level 4 — gap of 2 gradations."
    },
